t external to the J2EE architecture.  Consequently we need to develop ways to implement a loosely coupled integration of J2EE systems and a modern GIS system.  There are a number of ways to do this including: </p>
	<p>1.	Web Services<br />
2.	Adapters<br />
3.	Messaging
</p>
