3: Push the Add button and select Program.  This will bring up the file browser dialog.<br />
4: Browse to the <em>bin</em> directory of your ANT install and select <em>ant.bat</em>.<br />
5: Click Apply.  This should populate the tree with your new ANT tool.<br />
